title: 2010–11 Aruban Division di Honor
text:
In the 2010–11 season, the <a href="Aruban%20Division%20di%20Honor">Aruban Division di Honor</a> — the top-tier <a href="Association%20football">football</a> league in <a href="Aruba">Aruba</a> — consisted of ten teams. The championship was won by <a href="SV%20Racing%20Club%20Aruba">Racing Club</a>.
